          "title": "Cha Cha Real Smooth",
          "year": 2022,
          "note": "Cooper Raiff's second film. Sold to Apple TV+ for a reported $15 million."
        },
        {
          "title": "Speak No Evil",
          "year": 2022,
          "note": "Sold to Shudder; more on it below."
        },
