      "kind": "discussion",
      "heading": "The noisy ones that didn't land",
      "films": [
        {
          "title": "When You Finish Saving the World",
          "year": 2022,
          "note": "Jesse Eisenberg's opening-night premiere. Julianne Moore as a shelter-running do-gooder, Finn Wolfhard as the son who won't perform activism the way she wants him to. Called uneven but well-acted, with Billy Bryk singled out."
        },
        {
          "title": "Sharp Stick",
          "year": 2022,
          "note": "Lena Dunham's first film since Tiny Furniture, her first since Girls. Jennifer Jason Leigh, Taylor Page, and Kristine Froseth as a young woman exploring her sexuality. Both hosts liked pieces of it and neither fully bought the whole."
        }
      ]
    },
